[p 
	[b 
		"Glitches:
	]b
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Gas/electricity/water causes no damage if the game is paused for the frame it would usually do so.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Items reappear if you use the Tranceiver after collecting them.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Tank has no hit detection when at the very top of the screen, and can be walked straight through without taking damage.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Floor traps can be frozen by entering any of the menus.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" The Super Computer can be skipped by holding right as you enter the room.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	[b 
		"2 Deaths:
	]b
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" The first death is used to jump straight back to the ground floor of Building #1. This saves ~40 seconds.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" The second death puts me back at the rear of Building #1, where three trucks can be used in sequence to reach the last building. This makes the Compass unnecessary, and skips some backtracking after defeating Coward Duck
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	[b 
		"Minimal Items:
	]b
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Card #1, Card #2, Grenade Launcher, Card #3, B.B. Suit, Uniform, Card #4, Ammunition, Ammunition, Card #5, Card #6, Rocket Launcher, Ammunition, Card #7, Card #8
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" As far as I am aware, this is the absolute minimum required to complete the game.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
