	[b 
		"Other notes:
	]b
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Some screens take longer to load than others. This is also true when exiting the menus. Whenever it was necessary to equip something, I did so wherever the load time was shortest (The best places are inside a truck, an elevator, or a small one-doored room).
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" I tried to take this damage in the places where it saves the most time, and measured it so that I had minimal health before each death and at the end of the game.
		$LF
	]li
